---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — EnDroit" description="EnDroit was built by legal-tech enthusiasts to make French law accessible through short-form video. Our mission, team and story.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="badge">About us</div>
      <h1>Making the law<br/><em>accessible to everyone.</em></h1>
      <p class="page-lead">
        Legal information is locked inside dense court rulings, codes and academic
        papers. We believe short-form video is the most underrated tool for legal
        education in 2026 — and creators deserve a platform built for them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <span class="kicker">Our mission</span>
          <h2>Empower legal creators to teach 10× faster.</h2>
          <p>
            EnDroit was founded after watching law students spend whole weekends
            wrestling with CapCut just to publish a 60-second TikTok on tenant
            rights. The content was good. The tooling was not.
          </p>
          <p>
            We built EnDroit to invert the equation: the tooling fades into the
            background so the legal expertise can take center stage.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="kicker">Our principles</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:18px">What we believe</h2>
          <ul class="principles">
            <li><strong>Accuracy first.</strong> Every claim cites a source. Disclaimers are automatic.</li>
            <li><strong>Creator-owned.</strong> Your scripts, your videos, your audience. We don't lock you in.</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy by default.</strong> Minimal data, transparent processing, GDPR-ready.</li>
            <li><strong>European-first.</strong> Built in France, hosted in the EU, billed in EUR.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainable pricing.</strong> Single per-seat price. No surprise overages.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Story</div>
      <h2>From a single TikTok account to a creator platform.</h2>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="tl-item">
          <span class="tl-dot"></span>
          <div>
            <h4>Late 2025 · The original channel</h4>
            <p>Gillian, a French law-and-computer-science student, launches a TikTok channel to vulgarise French law. Within months, the channel grows past 100k views per month — but the production pipeline (CapCut + ChatGPT + manual posting) takes 4 hours per video.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <span class="tl-dot"></span>
          <div>
            <h4>Q1 2026 · The internal tool</h4>
            <p>An internal automation pipeline is built in TypeScript: script generation, Remotion rendering, multi-platform publishing. Production time drops from 4 hours to 35 minutes per video.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <span class="tl-dot"></span>
          <div>
            <h4>Q2 2026 · Other creators ask</h4>
            <p>French law students and small firms start asking how the channel produces 4 videos a day. The decision is made to turn the internal pipeline into a platform other creators can use.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <span class="tl-dot"></span>
          <div>
            <h4>Q3 2026 · Public beta</h4>
            <p>EnDroit opens its first waitlist. The platform is invitation-only while we iron out the rough edges. Beta seats prioritise creators who already publish regularly on legal topics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Team</div>
      <h2>People building EnDroit</h2>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="avatar avatar-gm">GM</div>
          <h3>Gillian Masse</h3>
          <span class="role">Founder · Engineering & Product</span>
          <p>Law and computer science student. Operates the original EnDroit channel. Writes the script and rendering engine.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="avatar avatar-soon">+</div>
          <h3>Open role</h3>
          <span class="role">Legal Content Lead</span>
          <p>We're looking for a French lawyer or paralegal to lead our disclaimer templates and source-verification engine. <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--accent)">Reach out</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="avatar avatar-soon">+</div>
          <h3>Open role</h3>
          <span class="role">Community & Beta Manager</span>
          <p>Part-time, remote, native French. You'd onboard beta creators, run the Discord, gather feedback. <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--accent)">Apply</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-strip">
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size:28px">Want to build with us?</h2>
          <p>We're hiring contractors and full-time team members. Or just say hello.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { padding: 72px 0 56px; }
  .page-hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
  .page-lead { font-size: 18px; max-width: 620px; line-height: 1.65; }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .kicker {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.8px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .two-col h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 30px; }
  .two-col p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .principles {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .principles li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding-left: 22px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .principles li::before {
    content: '◆';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 10px;
    top: 4px;
  }
  .principles strong { color: #fff; }

  /* ── Timeline ── */
  .timeline {
    margin-top: 36px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 6px;
    top: 8px;
    bottom: 8px;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), var(--border) 80%);
  }
  .tl-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -24px;
    top: 6px;
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }
  .tl-item h4 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .tl-item p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ── Team ── */
  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .team-card { text-align: left; padding: 28px; }
  .avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .avatar-gm { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D9A451, #B07042); color: #0F1E33; }
  .avatar-soon {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-strong);
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .team-card h3 { margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .team-card .role {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .team-card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }

  .cta-strip {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .cta-strip p { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; font-size: 15px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .two-col, .team-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .cta-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
